dcterms:description: A partially observed version of the MiniPacman environment where the agent navigates a maze, trying to eat all the food while avoiding being eaten by a ghost. The agent sees only a 5 × 5 window around itself.

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of sequences of images of MNIST digits, where each digit moves by one pixel in a chosen direction. The model is trained to learn the state and roll forward in jumps.
dcterms:title: Moving MNIST

dcterms:description: A dataset generated from a noisy harmonic oscillator, where the model observes a noisy version of the current position and attempts to predict future states.
dcterms:title: Noisy Harmonic Oscillator
